pinyin: Lu:4 ba4 · hua1 ji4 hu4 hang2

sentences.english: This screen shot shows the Green Dam content filtering software distributed in China.
sentences.chinese: 這個截屏顯示了在中國推廣的綠壩內容過濾軟件。

sentences.english: Green Dam filters words and images as well as web addresses.
sentences.chinese: 綠壩不僅能過濾網絡地址，也能過濾文字和圖片。
